# Build artifacts
*.prg
*.sym
*.bin
*.efo
*.pef
outline-64.d64
# Submission bundle output — regenerated by tools/bundle_submission.sh
submission/

# Spindle (extracted/built locally per-checkout)
spindle-2.3/
spindle-2.3.tgz
spindle-3.1/
spindle-3.1.zip

# Screenshots / scratch
*.png
# Exception: greets' koala backdrop source PNG (320x200 indexed,
# converted to .kla at build time / by hand via png_to_koala.py).
!parts/greets/backdrop.png

# Python cache
__pycache__/

# Local upstream archives / backups
KickAssembler.zip
# Ship just the KA jar (freeware, v5.25) so CI + a fresh `git clone &&
# ./build.sh` work without the theweb.dk download (its WAF 415s cloud IPs).
# Everything else under kickass/ (PDF, Examples, cfg) stays ignored.
kickass/*
!kickass/KickAss.jar
chargen.bin

# ...but DO ship the C64 chargen ROM in greets so `git clone &&
# ./build.sh` works out of the box. greets/interlude LoadBinary it
# at assembly time; without it a fresh checkout fails immediately.
!parts/greets/chargen.bin

# Same reason: ship the pre-baked sprite font so a fresh clone builds
# without needing python+Pillow to run tools/gen_font.py first.
!parts/greets/font.bin

# Derivative of font.bin — regenerated by 'python3 tools/font_png.py export'
parts/greets/font.png

# Spritemate KickAss-assembly export (intermediate). Round-trip via
# tools/font_txt.py to refresh font.bin from it; not source-of-truth.
parts/greets/font.txt
parts/friet-met-desire/

# sim6502 build artifacts (assembled per-run by tests/sim6502/run.sh)
tests/sim6502/*.prg
tests/sim6502/*.sym
